  "antifungals_cyp_note": {
    "_warning": "Azole antifungals (fluconazole, voriconazole, itraconazole) are strong CYP3A4 inhibitors. Increase rivaroxaban/apixaban levels significantly. Common in hepatobiliary surgery prophylaxis."
